.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE_INVOICE_PAID_AMOUNT_SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-paid-amount-skewness \- FEAT-2816 skewness of paid invoice amounts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-paid-amount-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the skewness of paid invoice amounts for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2816).
.PP
Output: JSON object with key \fBpaid_amount_skewness\fR and \fBcount\fR.
Returns \fBnull\fR when fewer than the required minimum samples are available.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning (1)
